Commandough’s Oktoberfest 2025
Saturday September 27th
Join us for an all-day Oktoberfest celebration at Commandough’s Pizza. We’re bringing the Bavarian spirit to Zephyrhills with food, music, and plenty of fun.
Where: Commandough’s Pizza – 5841 Gall Blvd, Zephyrhills
When: Saturday, September 27 | All Day
Here’s what to expect:
Games and contests, including stein-holding challenges  Themed costumes and a lively Oktoberfest atmosphere  Commandough’s favorites plus Bavarian inspired-twists
Live Music:
Matt Dallas will be performing from 5 PM to 8 PM to keep the party going into the evening.
Bring the family during the day for food and fun, then stick around as the music and energy build into the night. Costumes encouraged — show off your Oktoberfest style.
Don’t miss Zephyrhills’ most festive Oktoberfest celebration. Gather your friends, mark your calendar, and make it a day to remember.

Commandough's story
Founded in 2015 by Michael Weaver and the Clemens family, Commandough's opened its doors on February 6th, 2016, in Zephyrhills, Florida, with a dream to create a warm, inviting place where the community could come together over delicious pizza and cold beer.
In just a few short years, Commandough's has become a beloved institution, deeply rooted in the heart of Zephyrhills. Our commitment to quality food, drinks, and exceptional service has fostered a family-like atmosphere that welcomes everyone. We take pride in our humble beginnings and remain dedicated to maintaining the same values and quality that have brought us from then to now.
We invite you to join us at Commandough's Pizza to experience the warmth of our community, the quality of our food, and the passion that drives us every day. Come down soon and give us a try!
End Section 2
Start Section 4 Custom section
Our Team
Our kitchen staff are passionate about the art of pizza making, bringing both creativity and precision to every pie they craft.
Our waitstaff and management are dedicated to providing exceptional service and making every customer feel like a part of our family.
We believe in fostering a positive and inclusive work environment where every team member can thrive and contribute to the success of Commandough's.
Join us at Commandough's Pizza, where great food, friendly faces, and a welcoming atmosphere come together!
